<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[١٢٥٠٢]</span> يَزيدُ، والِدُ نُمَيْرٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>رَوَى عَنهُ ابنُه نُميرٌ، قالَه بَقيَّةُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يَرْوِي عنْ أَبي أُمَامةَ البَاهِليِّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>شَاميٌّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
